{"tid":744533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"child 登玻璃心 屌醫護 屌港女 屌業主 屌人有父幹 屌狀元","createTime":"2018-07-16T04:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T11:00:55.000Z","uid":15711,"like":398,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed42cc7411df793d90e29bc2497f8e8c6da7078","tid":744533,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"自己讀唔到醫，只好日日搵野屌醫護，想證明醫生都叻唔過你，自我感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n自己追唔到港女，只好話港女眼角高，全部係雞，但係香港每年仲有孩兩萬對新人結婚，仲有好多人追到港女架啵<br />\n<br />\n自己買唔到樓（無錯港樓係好唔合理好貴），只好日日屌人有父幹，完全抹殺大部份人都係自己努力儲首期，推晒落父幹到就唔關自己事，係父母錯社會錯<br />\n<br />\n自己做唔到狀元，人地做狀元又要起人父母底做咩職業，無人高要做狀元先得，但咁眼紅狀元就好有問題啦<br />\n<br />\n連登淪落到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7423032bdb7f08f3a8b3022c84ac2c19499d994f","tid":744533,"uid":154054,"like":91,"dislike":4,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"屌埋樓主"},{"pid":"f00b52e05b43efa720b5025f4479f3edd5a609ae","tid":744533,"uid":141151,"like":62,"dislike":8,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"根本有人搞分化，想撕裂成個香港"},{"pid":"f5a8be81fc2691da90d103238847a346cbcee4e1","tid":744533,"uid":15711,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"7423032bdb7f08f3a8b3022c84ac2c19499d994f","tid":744533,"uid":154054,"like":91,"dislike":4,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"屌埋樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"隨便啦，child 登有邊日唔鬧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b068a32afb0a10799576e9a6f00c6bca55f183","tid":744533,"uid":166725,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"連登太多葡萄撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6933bf2772c1f676b99167b7342c918aff83ab23","tid":744533,"uid":189053,"like":28,"dislike":23,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04cb586570c42dc0cb43b3f35ea999a99814cfd4","tid":744533,"uid":177